data.description: Don't miss your opportunity on this charming downtown home. Conveniently located, this historically built 1919 home boasts of many original features. Appreciation for original wood floors, built-ins, moldings & trim can be found throughout. 1340 sq ft with three spacious bedrooms and walk in closets. Nice sized living room with a formal dining area. Spacious Kitchen and pantry. Great investment opportunity! Call today to schedule a viewing! Selling AS IS.
